data.description: Absolutely gorgeous single-level townhome, prime Phoenix location in the beautiful 8th Street Square community close to shopping, entertainment, restaurants. Conveniently located just steps from sparkling community pool. Home features vaulted ceiling, clerestory windows in main living area for open, spacious feel. Gorgeous stacked stone wood-burning fireplace in living room, & sliding glass doors to large private patio, an ideal space to relax & entertain. Freshly painted interior in designer colors. Large open kitchen, gleaming SS appliances, tons of bright white cabinetry, sparkling counters. Huge primary bedroom, large walk-in closet. Bathrooms are elegant & well appointed, new vanities, quartz, custom mirrors. Secondary bedrooms both very spacious, plus large laundry room. Don't miss! Current loan is assumable at 3.0%, approx. $355K balance.
